овий інструмент – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ph%C3%A1i_sinh_t%C3%A0i_ch%C3%ADnh" title="Phái sinh tài chính – Vietnamese" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh-yue"><a href="https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7" title="金融衍生工具 – Cantonese" lang="zh-yue" hreflang="zh-yue" class="interlanguage-link-target">粵語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E8%A1%8D%E7%94%9F%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7" title="金融衍生工具 – Chinese" lang="zh" hreflang="zh" class="interlanguage-link-target">中文</a></li>					</ul>
